Model

\[\begin{align} \text{mean rate of rates} &= \frac{\text{max score}}{\text{max duration}} = \frac{100 \text{ points}}{15 \text{ minutes}} \\ \text{rate of rates} &= \frac{1}{\text{mean rate of rates}} \\ \\ \text{rate}^{\text{blue}} &\sim \text{Exponential}(\text{rate of rates}) \\ \text{rate}^{\text{red}} &\sim \text{Exponential}(\text{rate of rates}) \\ \\ \text{ttp}^{\text{blue}}_i &= \text{time}^{\text{blue}}_i - \text{time}^{\text{blue}}_{i-1} \\ \text{ttp}^{\text{red}}_i &= \text{time}^{\text{red}}_i - \text{time}^{\text{red}}_{i-1} \\ \\ \text{ttp}^{\text{blue}}_i &\sim \text{Exponential}(\text{rate}^{\text{blue}}) \\ \text{ttp}^{\text{red}}_i &\sim \text{Exponential}(\text{rate}^{\text{red}}) \end{align}\]
